354
00:23:29,825 --> 00:23:33,286
They'd be spent in sweet content
Dreaming away

355
00:23:33,704 --> 00:23:35,663
When skies are gray
When skies are blue

356
00:23:35,873 --> 00:23:37,665
Morning, noon and nighttime too

357
00:23:37,875 --> 00:23:41,878
All I do the whole day through
