Let the stormy clouds chase

1451
01:40:49,919 --> 01:40:51,253
Stop that girl!

1452
01:40:51,462 --> 01:40:53,421
That girl running up the aisle!
Stop her!

1453
01:40:53,631 --> 01:40:56,299
That's the girl whose voice
you heard and loved.

1454
01:40:56,467 --> 01:40:59,511
She's the real star of the picture,
Kathy Selden!

